local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["inexhaustible"]={"inexhaustible","[ɪnɪg'zɔːstɪb(ə)l; ɪneg-]","[,ɪnɪɡ'zɔstəbl]","adj.用不完的",'adj.用不完的(无穷的,不知疲倦的)','I shall die again and again to know that life is inexhaustible.','我将死了又死，以明白生是无穷无尽的。','He is immortal, not because he alone among creatures has an inexhaustible voice, but because he has a soul, a spirit capable of compassion, and sacrifice, and endurance.','人类不朽不是因为在万物中唯有他能永远发言、而是因为他有灵魂，有同情心、有牺牲和忍耐精神。'}
